WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:181083,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

00:28:57.571 --> 00:29:03.644 align:start position:23% line:-2
そんな方のためにiOS 12の
新しいAPIをご紹介します

00:29:04.111 --> 00:29:08.615 align:start position:2% line:-2
ASWebAuthenticationSessionの
機能を説明します

00:29:10.851 --> 00:29:12.753 align:start position:32% line:-1
Shinyに戻ります

00:29:12.953 --> 00:29:16.089 align:start position:23% line:-2
今回はexample.comを
選びます

00:29:16.190 --> 00:29:18.292 align:start position:36% line:-1
有名なSNSです

00:29:19.893 --> 00:29:21.628 align:start position:38% line:-1
タップすると―

00:29:21.728 --> 00:29:26.200 align:start position:29% line:-2
アプリケーションが
新しいAPIを通知します

00:29:26.633 --> 00:29:31.271 align:start position:29% line:-2
このAPIで
ログインが早まる理由は―

00:29:31.371 --> 00:29:34.274 align:start position:20% line:-2
Safariとのcookie情報の
共有です

00:29:35.075 --> 00:29:37.411 align:start position:32% line:-1
もちろん その前に―

00:29:37.511 --> 00:29:40.214 align:start position:29% line:-1
ユーザーの同意が必要です

00:29:41.682 --> 00:29:45.719 align:start position:16% line:-2
安全なView Controllerが
同意後に提供され―

00:29:45.819 --> 00:29:49.389 align:start position:27% line:-1
認証連携の手続きに進みます

00:29:50.457 --> 00:29:55.896 align:start position:16% line:-2
iPhoneでexample.comに
ログインしているので―

00:29:55.996 --> 00:29:57.898 align:start position:36% line:-1
“許可”をタップ

00:29:59.800 --> 00:30:00.367 align:start position:46% line:-1
よし

